\dn song fi:a capella, sung by a man by himself (fl:opp. fv:n-eh_ba-laklak 'dance song', interpreted by several singers and accompanied by music)
\rf
\ue
\ee Désigne en particu^lier certains genres de chants, fl:ex. fv:vawelop.
